text:
Preds ready for three games at home this week 
Updated: Tue, Oct 20 2015, 04:38 PM 
Stream WZTV Fox 17 Newscasts LIVE starting with Fox 17 This Morning at 4:30am, News at 5:30pm and News at 9pm & 10 pm 
The Predators are back in Nashville after a successful road trip, winning two games out of three. Tuesday night, the Preds open a three game home stand.
